    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "For now, untill we make instantsearch-react (this is currently being worked on), I advise you if you need to add a \"add to cart\" button to add it into your hits template and then if you need to bind an action on it, either use the old time onClick=window.action OR use event delegation https://davidwalsh.name/event-delegate\n\nIf you have any idea on how to make instantsearch.js better integrate with meteor.js templating I would be happy to know them!\n\nLet me know if the dirty solution works for now\n",
