    "body": "Unfortunately, Meteor uses template based routing. So, when I try to insert the widgets, I always get this type of error: `utils.js:79Uncaught Error: Container must be \"string\" or \"HTMLElement\". Unable to find #hits`\n\nAny solutions you can think of? \n\nI've tried everything I could think of and nothing worked. \n",
